        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Literature value/calculated value. Valid for 2011.
Based on Stolz&amp;Frischknecht 2015, Tables 3.7, 3.6 and the SBB railway electricity mix from Itten et al. 2012 Table 3.182.
A loss of 5% from gross to net is assumed for oil power.


Stolz, P., Frischnkecht, R. 2015. Umweltbilanz Strommix Schweiz 2011. Issued by treeze Ltd. for the Federal Office for the Environment, Switzerland. 

Itten, R., Frischknecht, R., Stucki, M. 2012. Life Cycle Inventories of Electricity Mixes and Grid. ESU-services Ltd., fair conulting in sustainability, Uster. " </productionVolumeComment>
